                    <span>I had to read this book for a school project, and let's just say it was pretty bad. I've read many better survival stories that were a little more realistic than this. But, Hatchet has taught me a lesson: Pay attention to all that's around...you'll never know when you'll end up in a situation like Brian's.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I liked it</div>
