                    <span>The book is basically like a self-journey. The main character did his best to live in the wilderness with harsh conditions the best he could. He was physically beaten by large massive animals, bitten by many mosquitoes, and the anticipation to leave. He also wondered about the situation with his mother and her mysterious lover. I would suggest everyone to read this book.</span>
                  
              
